			<div class="gta-horizontal-featured--single">
				<div class="gta-horizontal-featured--inner">
											<div class="gta-horizontal-featured--image">
							<a href="https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/blogs/africasource/coronavirus-comes-to-sudan/"><img src="//www.atlanticcouncil.org/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/32438075892_2620000263_o-500x350.jpg" alt="African leaders respond to coronavirus&#8230; on Twitter" class="lazy lazy-hidden gta-horizontal-featured--img"><noscript><img src="https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/32438075892_2620000263_o-500x350.jpg" alt="African leaders respond to coronavirus&#8230; on Twitter" class="gta-horizontal-featured--img"></noscript></a>
						</div>
										<div class="gta-horizontal-featured--content">
						<p class="gta-horizontal-featured--heading">Mon, Mar 30, 2020</p>
						<h4 class="gta-horizontal-featured--title"><a href="https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/blogs/africasource/coronavirus-comes-to-sudan/">Coronavirus comes to Sudan</a></h4>
						<div class="gta-horizontal-featured--excerpt"><p>Not yet one year into a historic political transition and in the midst of an economic collapse, Sudan’s future was already hanging in the balance.  The addition of a national and global public health crisis now has the potential for a ‘make or break’ impact on the country. </p></div>
													<p class="gta-horizontal-featured--tax">
																	<span class="gta-horizontal-featured--tax--cats">AfricaSource</span>
																									<span class="gta-horizontal-featured--tax--connect">by</span>
																									<a class="gta-site-banner--tax--expert gta-post-site-banner--tax--expert" href="https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/expert/cameron-hudson/">Cameron Hudson</a>								
							</p>
																			<div class="gta-horizontal-featured--terms">
																	<a class="s-pill small" href="https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/region/africa/">Africa</a>
																	<a class="s-pill small" href="https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/issue/coronavirus/">Coronavirus</a>
