						</div>
										<div class="gta-horizontal-featured--content">
						<p class="gta-horizontal-featured--heading">Thu, Mar 26, 2020</p>
						<h4 class="gta-horizontal-featured--title"><a href="https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/blogs/africasource/a-rough-road-ahead-for-nigeria/">A rough road ahead for Nigeria</a></h4>
						<div class="gta-horizontal-featured--excerpt"><p>Africa’s giant, Nigeria, is awakening to a new economic and social reality as a result of the coronavirus crisis. The country of two hundred million has already recorded over fifty cases and its first COVID-related death. News of high-profile infectees is starting to drive social change and spur calls for stronger government action.</p></div>
